'''''Acholeplasma phage MV-L51''''' ('''L51''') is a [[virus]] species.  It is the [[type species]] of the [[plectrovirus]] genus.<ref name="TidonaDarai2011">{{Cite book|author1=Christian Tidona|author2=Gholamreza Darai|title=The Springer Index of Viruses|date=13 October 2011|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-0-387-95919-1|page=751}}</ref>

